_sText:
This is a map made to make easier the process to unlock the "Defuse this" achievementÂ 
Instruccions:
-The basics to add a new custom map
-Only add one bot
-Max difficult
-Buy a granade
-Shoot him 3-4 times with the starter pistol
-Distract him with the weird geometry
-Let him hurt you until you have below 30HP
-Plant the bomb
-Activate your granade
-Hold your granade and let him kill you
-Enjoy

BTW the original map name is "de_mapa_tocho"
